          %strong Games, Webquests, and More
        %p Learning about money can be both fun and educational. Webquests can take you from website to website on a learning journey about finance. You can pretend that you are earning money and learn how to budget it. You can even explore a shopping mall to make decisions about what you buy from different stores. Learn about the history of United States currency to see how it has changed over the years. Or try an activity where you run a professional sports team and have to take care of its budget.
